headline: Fair Isaac Corporation Announces Date for Reporting of First Quarter Fiscal 2025 Financial Results
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., January 21, 2025--Global analytics software leader, FICO, will announce its first quarter fiscal 2025 results on February 4, 2025, after the market closes and will host a conference call on February 4th at 5:00 p.m. Eastern time (4:00 p.m. Central/2:00 p.m. Pacific).
